import React, { Component } from 'react';
import {ListGroup, Card, Button} from 'react-bootstrap';
import mino from '../assets/mino.png';
import mino2 from '../assets/mino-copy.png';

export class ProductList extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <ListGroup>
                <ListGroup.Item style={{borderStyle:"none"}}>
                    <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
                        <Card.Img variant="top" src={`${mino}`} style={{objectFit:"fill"}}/>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Denumire produs</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                            Pret produs
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary">Adaugă în coș</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                </ListGroup.Item>
                <ListGroup.Item style={{borderStyle:"none"}}>
                    <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
                        <Card.Img variant="top" src={`${mino2}`} style={{objectFit:"fill"}}/>
                        <Card.Body>
                            <Card.Title>Denumire produs</Card.Title>
                            <Card.Text>
                            Pret produs
                            </Card.Text>
                            <Button variant="primary">Adaugă în coș</Button>
                        </Card.Body>
                    </Card>
                </ListGroup.Item>
            </ListGroup>
        )
    }
}
